help.output-sending-dm-failed: [U|u]nable to send you a DM. Check if you have DMs disabled and try again.
help.output-no-command: [U|u]nable to identify command. Use {{usage}} to view the list of all commands.
help.output-heading-dm:
[T|t]o run a command in any server, use {{guild_usage}}. For example, {{example}}. To run a command in this DM, simply use {{dm_usage}} without a prefix.

Use {{detailed_help}} to view detailed information about a specific command.
Use {{all_help}} to view a list of *all* commands, not just available ones.

Use {{all_help}} to view a list of *all* commands, not just available ones.

prefix.output-admin-only: [O|o]nly administrators may change the command prefix.
prefix.output-owner-only: [O|o]nly the bot owner(s) may change the global command prefix.
prefix.output-reset-default: [T|t]he command prefix has been reset to the default prefix (currently {{default}}). $t(utils:prefix.run-commands)
prefix.output-set-prefix: [T|t]he command prefix has been set to `{{prefix}}`. $t(utils:prefix.run-commands)
